com.sun.identity.wsfederation.logging

Class LogUtil

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sun.identity.wsfederation.logging.LogUtil

  • public abstract class LogUtil
extends Object
    The LogUtil class defines methods which are used by WS-Federation component to write logs.

    • Method Detail

      • access

        public static void access(Level level,
                          String msgid,
                          String[] data)
        Logs message to ID-FF access logs.
        Parameters:
        level - the log level , these are based on those defined in java.util.logging.Level, the values for level can be any one of the following :
        • SEVERE (highest value)
        • WARNING
        • INFO
        • CONFIG
        • FINE
        • FINER
        • FINEST (lowest value)
        msgid - the message or a message identifier.
        data - string array of dynamic data to be replaced in the message.

      • access

        public static void access(Level level,
                          String msgid,
                          String[] data,
                          Object session)
        Logs message to ID-FF access logs.
        Parameters:
        level - the log level , these are based on those defined in java.util.logging.Level, the values for level can be any one of the following :
        • SEVERE (highest value)
        • WARNING
        • INFO
        • CONFIG
        • FINE
        • FINER
        • FINEST (lowest value)
        msgid - the message or a message identifier.
        data - string array of dynamic data to be replaced in the message.
        session - the User's session object

      • isAccessLoggable

        public static boolean isAccessLoggable(Level level)
        Checks if an access message of the given level would actually be logged by this logger. This check is based on the Loggers effective level.
        Parameters:
        level - a message logging level.
        Returns:
        true if the given message level is currently being logged.

      • isErrorLoggable

        public static boolean isErrorLoggable(Level level)

        Parameters:
        level - a message logging level.
        Returns:
        true if the given message level is currently being logged.
